    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a sentient Vegetable who can transform into 6 different veggies with unique abilities. Escape the tormenting lab where you were created and are now being held captive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257040/extras/76cdf64e99ca52b7f405f005802a5bc1.avif?t=1752354193\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CARROT: </strong>Dash through the air and see in the dark using the carrot’s abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOMATO:</strong> Climb the ancient vines that have spread around the lab and micro-verses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BROCCOLI: </strong>Swing through the air with the Broccoli’s grappling hook ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PEPPER:</strong> Melt Ice with this fire-y ability!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUCUMBER:</strong> Dive into sand to move extra quickly and avoid hazardous elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EGGPLANT: </strong>Break rocks and manipulate the environment through smashing stones and boulders to bits with the physically strongest veggie of them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257040/extras/6fc58e0f0cc81561c10bdeb1f3c3ffb6.poster.avif?t=1752354193\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257040/extras/6fc58e0f0cc81561c10bdeb1f3c3ffb6.webm?t=1752354193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257040/extras/6fc58e0f0cc81561c10bdeb1f3c3ffb6.mp4?t=1752354193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257040/extras/6fd6d0de28f80522390dc542dd517a91.avif?t=1752354193\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse terrain and environment </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 “hot-swappable” veggies with different &amp; unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectable DNA strands that unlock new abilities</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
